  "texts": [
    "Goal & Research QuestionsThe study aims to explore methods for efficiently developing new services that meet user needs.",
    "Specifically, we propose a system that extracts 6W1H needs related to unknown services using the interactive needs extraction system.",
    "Keywords representing the characteristics of these needs are then extracted using an LLM and searched within the SUCCEED system to obtain upcycling cases that aid in fulfilling these needs [24,25].",
    "This study aims to answer the following three Research Questions (RQs) through the implementation and experimentation of the proposed method:• RQ1: How can the services desired by users be identified?• RQ2: How are user needs characterized?",
    "• RQ3: How can insights useful for developing desired services be obtained from user input?"
  ],
